data.description: Welcome home 4046 Balboa-luxurious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhome provides space for a modern life style-features open floor plan- living/dining area w/tons of natural light-cozy kitchen w/stainless steel appliances -a master suite w/an en suite bathroom walk-in closet-two additional bedrooms have plenty of space for family or guests-with a bonus room between the 2 bedrooms which makes a great play area or media room-The townhome also boast wood floors on main level carpet on 2nd floor-a large two-car garage-a private backyard patio perfect for entertaining-no back neighbors-This is the perfect home for any family looking for the perfect combination of style and comfort located in the award winning Meridiana Subdivision-Amenities include lazy river with wave pool-2 gyms-family & kiddie pool-tennis, basketball, volleyball courts-numerous play grounds-lakes you can fish in-pickle ball court-from daycare all way thru high school your children never have to leave the subdivision
